  <md:title>Demand and Supply Shifts in Foreign Exchange Markets</md:title>
  <md:abstract><para id="para-00001">By the end of this section, you will be able to:</para><list id="list-00001">
<item>Explain supply and demand for exchange rates</item>
<item>Define arbitrage</item>
<item>Explain purchasing power parity's importance when comparing countries.</item>
</list></md:abstract>
